    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="update">Last Updated: June 2023</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We collect information you provide directly, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Account information (username, email, profile details)</li>
        <li>Study preferences and academic interests</li>
        <li>Group participation and scheduling data</li>
        <li>Communication content within study groups</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Information</h2>
    <p>Your data helps us:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
        <li>Personalize your study group recommendations</li>
        <li>Facilitate communication between study partners</li>
        <li>Analyze usage patterns for product improvement</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. Information may be shared with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Other group members (only what's necessary for collaboration)</li>
        <li>Service providers who assist our operations (under strict confidentiality)</li>
        <li>When required by law or to protect our rights</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Your Choices</h2>
    <p>You can:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Review and update account information</li>
        <li>Control visibility of your profile details</li>
        <li>Opt-out of non-essential communications</li>
        <li>Request account deletion</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Security</h2>
    <p>We implement appropriate measures to protect your information, but no system is completely secure.</p>

    <h2>6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy and will notify users of significant changes.</p>

    <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related questions: <a href="contact.html">Contact Form</a></p>
